*_allregions.csv

# Generated reports
report.md
report.html
report_regions.md
report_regions.html

# Run logs
run_*.log

# Subject lists (sensitive; match the existing convention at 04_secondlevel_group/ root)
*sublist*

# One-off / scratch
test_output.csv

# Backups
*.bak
